description:
The grand finale is here as Captain America faces off against a very nasty HYDRA horde…and unwittingly holds the fate of a young boy in the balance! The newest Ant-Man, Eric O’Grady, has never been a team player but will his new position amidst the ranks of Earth’s Mightiest Heroes be his redemption…or a one way ticket to the bench?! And Thor brightens up the Young Avengers day in a very special story brought to you by the legendary Alan Davis!

Story Titles

  • Captain America in "A Little Help"
  • Ant-Man in "Growing"
  • The Young Avengers in "Rain Stops Play"
name: A Little Help; Growing; Rain Stops Play
